## SECTION 5: KNOWN BUGS (fix before anything else)
## ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

BUGS_TO_FIX:
  [x] BUG_1: server.js uses better-sqlite3 API (synchronous) but package is sqlite3 (async)
  [x] BUG_2: database.js never creates data/ directory → DB init fails
  [x] BUG_3: package.json missing "start" and "dev" scripts
  [x] BUG_4: io.emit() called before socket server confirmed up → race condition
  [x] BUG_5: assets/css/main.css is empty → ALL styling broken
  [x] BUG_6: Passwords stored in plain text
  [x] BUG_7: JWT_SECRET has insecure fallback 'rrdch-secret'
  [x] BUG_8: appointments.html form has no JS validation or handler
  [x] BUG_9: Missing data-kn attributes on many elements → Kannada toggle broken
  [x] BUG_10: Express v5 installed but code not v5 compatible
  [x] BUG_11: login.html has no role-based redirect
  [x] BUG_12: events.html uses static HTML, not FullCalendar.js
  [x] BUG_13: virtual-tour.html missing Pannellum CDN in <head>
  [x] BUG_14: Dark mode JS handler missing
  [x] BUG_15: portals/ folder entirely empty

## ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
## SECTION 6: TECH STACK REFERENCE
## ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

FRONTEND_STACK:
  HTML: Semantic HTML5 (no frameworks — pure HTML/CSS/JS for GitHub Pages)
  CSS: Custom design system (main.css) + AOS animations
  JS: Vanilla ES6+ (no React/Vue — keeps it deployable to GitHub Pages)
  Fonts: Playfair Display (headings) + Noto Sans Kannada (Kannada mode)
  Icons: Font Awesome 6
  Calendar: FullCalendar.js v6
  Tour: Pannellum.js v2.5.6
  Charts: Chart.js (in portals only)
  Dates: Flatpickr
  Toasts: Toastify.js
  Animations: AOS (Animate on Scroll)
  AI Chat: Direct Anthropic API fetch (no server proxy needed for demo)

BACKEND_STACK:
  Runtime: Node.js v20+ LTS
  Framework: Express.js v4.18.2 (PINNED to v4, NOT v5)
  Database: SQLite via sqlite3 (async/callback) for hackathon
  Auth: jsonwebtoken + bcrypt
  Real-time: Socket.IO v4
  File uploads: multer
  Email: nodemailer (Gmail SMTP)
  Validation: express-validator
  Rate limiting: express-rate-limit
  Logging: morgan
  Environment: dotenv

