## HOW TO USE THIS FILE
## ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
## 1. At the START of every new session, copy-paste this entire file into your AI assistant
## 2. The AI will read PHASE_STATUS and LAST_SESSION_DATE to know what's been done
## 3. At the END of every session, update LAST_SESSION_DATE, LAST_COMPLETED_PHASE,
##    and NEXT_TODO so the next session can continue seamlessly
## 4. When a phase is complete, change [ ] to [x] in PHASE_STATUS
